{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4b8f5b6d9b","title":"在抗大校务办公会议上的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"79bf1a602d","index":0,"year":1935,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"4b8f5b6d9b"}],"tags":[{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji8","name":"毛泽东全集第8卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji8.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji8":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f8ed510392","type":"paragraph","text":"在抗大校务办公会议上的讲话口","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"4b8f5b6d9b"},{"id":"8a7cc032cc","type":"paragraph","text":"（1935年）我们要来一个读书比赛，看谁读的书多，掌握的知识多。只要是书，不管是中国的，外国的，古典的，现代的，正面的，反面的，大家都可以涉猎。但不能一目十行。…读书先是粗读，有个大概的印象，然后是复读，重温一下重要章节，也叫精读。在这个基础上再写点读书笔记，问几个为什么，联系实际思考一下周围的事情。这样才能防止教条主义和本本主义","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"4b8f5b6d9b"},{"id":"4c565c64f8","type":"paragraph","text":"这是毛泽东在抗大校务办公会议上讲话的一部分。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"4b8f5b6d9b"}],"page":{"id":"7d02829308","publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"4b8f5b6d9b","start":186,"end":186}}}},"__N_SSG":true}